sections.heading: to 69-23-19 - Repealed.
sections.text: Repeals.— Laws 1987, ch. 234, § 84 repealed 69-23-1 to 69-23-19 NMSA 1978, as enacted by Laws 1933, ch. 153, §§ 157, 158, 160 to 165, 167 to 169, 171, and 173 to 175, relating to electrical equipment in coal mines, effective July 1, 1987. For present comparable provisions,see69-8-1 to 69-8-15 NMSA 1978.
